{"tid":1544053,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"移民政策係好多地方都係大議題、點解香港幾乎冇人理？","createTime":"2019-09-05T12:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T10:42:31.000Z","uid":89861,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e3a099ef9180b37a8eb4899af740579b9d28ae16","tid":1544053,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"香港好多問題都係源至於移民政策，包括最大既房屋問題、上年香港由大陸移居香港人數成9萬人（包括讀書、短期工作），比出生人口仲要多，我諗呢個世界都冇幾多個地方外來人口比本地出生人口多～<br />\n<br />\n可能你會以為全部係源至於單程証、我地政府冇權話事～但事實上單程証人數係4萬幾人、另外個4萬幾人係我地既扑街政府審批來香港，我地絕對可以爭取<br />\n<br />\n一年9萬人來港，香港需要幾多屋先夠？<br />\n如果再唔停移民，香港樓價只會無止境升上去，唔通真係要迫本地後生仔搬去大灣區？"},{"pid":"abeeea30c5f175a3d5bd1fe7645d4a6233ad6ac4","tid":1544053,"uid":305794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:03:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">［幫手推到置頂］9月8日 美領人鏈防鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544032</a><br />\n跪求各位巴絲幫手推一推<del>（我係一個有夢想既P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</del><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aeee406a2ee0a2803713c588b04735d5379f1cb","tid":1544053,"uid":262717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:08:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97e3d83afe982c80f343c183125ea9a97e3b6c8b","tid":1544053,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:45:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39b35b004fc5ef793ec9913db380910becf267c5","tid":1544053,"uid":60694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:56:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾 ，港共一年有邊日唔係做緊仆街野？我地唔撚係要同佢逐個爭取撤回阿，我